        "ggv20YPCwvh_text": "<p>I'm always cautious when recommending masks, <strong>as many contain ingredients that can irritate sensitive skin.</strong> This mask stands out because of its minimal and gentle formula. <strong>It's designed to be well-tolerated by a wide range of skin types, offering a soothing and calming experience even for those with reactive skin.</strong></p>",
